tool_description: Out address autocopmlete APIs allow your users to typeahead USPS verified addresses, cities and zipcodes. Our APIs are fast and affordable. Suggestions are available for abbreviated or full street type and direction (i.e. north or n, northwest or nw, apartment or apt or #). Suggestions also includes unit numbers. First 100,000 requests per month are free of charge. Please visit https://sthan.io for more details.
name: autocomplete usa
title: autocomplete usa

api_list.name: Autocomplete Zipcode
api_list.description:
1.  DisplayType = 0 gives output like "XXXXX, CityName, StateCode"
2.  DisplayType = 1 gives output like "XXXXX, CityName, FullStateName"
3.  DisplayType = 2 gives output like "XXXXX-YYYY, CityName, StateCode"
4.  DisplayType = 3 gives output like "XXXXX-YYYY, CityName, FullStateName"
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://autocomplete-usa.p.rapidapi.com/marketplace/autocomplete/usa/zipcode/displayType/0/4323"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "autocomplete-usa.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
